show.description: A wealthy couple, Shalini and Mukesh Saxena, are mistaken for frauds during a resort getaway, triggering a storm of humiliation and cruelty by a power-hungry manager. But when the truth about their identity explodes, it sets off a dramatic reckoning proving that respect can’t be bought, and karma comes with interest. Watch Now!
